  <!-- EN: Stugna missile launcher -->
  <DMSAC_StugnaATGM.label>短號導彈發射器</DMSAC_StugnaATGM.label>
  <!-- EN: A single-use anti-tank guided missile designed to be fired and discarded. effective against heavy mechs and even tanks. however to lock on target, it requires a long aiming time and clear line of sight. -->
  <DMSAC_StugnaATGM.description>設計為用後即丟的一次性反坦克導彈發射裝置。對付重型機甲乃至主力戰車都十分有效。然而要鎖定目標需要較長的瞄準時間和清晰的射擊視野。</DMSAC_StugnaATGM.description>
