  <!-- EN: An anti-tank missile launcher platform that can be deployed and operated remotely. It will stop functioning once its battery runs out or no available rounds. If damaged sufficiently, it may explode. -->
  <DMSAC_Turret_StugnaATGM.description>一種代號為雪橇的便攜式遙控反坦克發射平台，能夠裝載並發射短號反坦克導彈，基於遙控方式操控可以有效避免射手暴露於直接的危險中，然而發射裝置有被EMP與煙霧干擾的風險。</DMSAC_Turret_StugnaATGM.description>
